snippet.title: Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai | B Praak | Nawazuddin Siddiqui | Shehnaaz Gill | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents ‘Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai’, the second single from B Praak’s debut album, “Zohrajabeen”. Reuniting after their super hit 'Baarish Ki Jaaye', the all-star team of Nawazuddin Siddiqui, BPraak, Jaani, and Arvindr Khaira is back with yet another heart-wrenching song that explores the complexities of romance, and the pain of its absence. Experience a melancholic journey in the voice of BPraak paired with soul-stirring lyrics and composition by Jaani and a short film by Arvindr Khaira featuring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Shehnaaz Gill that embodies a bittersweet tale that can't be chased anymore, painting a picture of respectful regret. Indulge your feelings in the beauty of this musical masterpiece, as it leaves you reflecting upon the significance of love and the poignancy of letting go. 

Listen to ‘Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai’ on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/YKSHH

snippet.title: ഈ ഉമ്മയും മോനും കടന്നു  വന്ന വഴികൾ  ! | @noufalftkd2822 | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
ഈ ഉമ്മയേം മോനെയും അറിയാത്തവർ കുറവായിരിക്കും. നൗഫൽ ആൻഡ് ഉമ്മ എന്ന ചാനലിലൂടെ മലയാളികൾക്ക് സുപരിചിതരാണ് ഇവർ രണ്ടുപേരും. ജീവിതത്തിൽ ഒത്തിരി കഷ്ടപാടുകളെയും വെല്ലുവിളികളെയും അതീജീവിച്ചവരാണ് ഇവർ രണ്ടുപേരും. സ്വന്തം  മക്കളേ കൊല്ലാൻ കൊണ്ടുപോകേണ്ട അവസ്ഥ പോലും ഈ ഉമ്മക്ക് ഉണ്ടായി . കേൾക്കാം ഉമ്മയുടെയും  മോന്റെയും കഥ. 

Introducing Noufal and Umma, two individuals who have become beloved figures among Malayalis. The situation of even wanting to kill their own children has occurred in Umma's life. Their lives have been marked by incredible struggles, making their story one that resonates deeply with all who hear it.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

#joshtalksmalayalam #motivation  #nevergiveup

snippet.title: ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രായം കുറഞ്ഞ മജീഷ്യൻ മലപ്പുറത്തു കാരൻ.
snippet.description:
#baseworld
#magic
#മാജിഷ്യൻ
#magician
#kottakal
#small
#smallmagician
#little
#arjun
 Malappuram Kottakkal എന്ന സ്ഥലത്തുള്ള ഒരു വീഡിയോ ആണ് ഇന്ന് നിങ്ങൾ കണ്ടുകൊണ്ടിരിക്കുന്നത് ഏകദേശം അഞ്ചു വയസ്സ് മാത്രം പ്രായമുള്ള അർജുൻ ഇന്ന് മാജിക് കലയെ വളരെ വലിയൊരു സംഭവമായി മാറ്റിയിരിക്കുന്നു ഇവന്റെ ഈയൊരു പ്രായത്തിൽ ഇപ്പോൾ ആരും മാജിക് ഇതുപോലെ കാണിക്കുന്നില്ല എന്നതാണ് യാഥാർത്ഥ്യം. ഏതായാലും ഈ കുഞ്ഞിനെ സപ്പോർട്ട് ചെയ്യേണ്ടത് നമ്മുടെ കടമയാണ് അതുകൊണ്ട് വീഡിയോ മാക്സിമം ഷെയർ ചെയ്യുക അതുപോലെ ചാനൽ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യുക

 ഇതുപോലുള്ള കഴിവുകൾ ഉള്ള കുട്ടികളെയും അതുപോലെതന്നെ ആളുകളെ ഞങ്ങളിലേക്ക് എത്തിക്കുന്നതിനുവേണ്ടി ബേസ് വേൾഡ് കോൺടാക്ട് നമ്പർ 7736433046

ലത്തീഫ് ക്കയുടെ മാജിക്‌ ടീമിന്റെ show നിങ്ങൾക്കും ആസ്വദിക്കണമെന്നുണ്ടെങ്കിൽ താഴെ കാണുന്ന നമ്പറിൽ ബുക്ക്‌ ചെയ്യാവുന്നതാണ്

VIZMANIA  magic and mentalism SHOW

9961 100 222
9947 031 045

snippet.title: Manipur: Village Stranded In The Middle Of Firing, Residents Run For Cover
snippet.description:
Mojo Story team reached Khoijuman Tabi, an interior village in Bishnupur district of Manipur allegedly under attack by Kukis. While we talked to people in the village, we could hear heavy gunshots. Our team saw young boys (can be termed as militants however the villagers say the boys are just volunteers who guard their village) from the village with modern weapons moving towards the firing site to guard their village. The women of the village lined up and showered blessings by kissing the forehead of the militants before they left for the fight. Mojo Story shoot was interrupted at number of times as the villagers objected capturing the critical moments such as young boys moving with weapons in the village. A village source said, these might be the guns looted from the police stations in Manipur.

#manipur #kuki #meitei

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 17 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 3rd July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Hero-made new Harley Davidson X440 | Rs 2.29 Lacs | All Details
snippet.description: Here's all you need to know about the brand new Harley Davidson X440 that has been launched in India at a starting price of Rs 2.29 lacs (ex-showroom). The top-end variant, X440 S, costs Rs 2.69 lacs (ex-showroom). It will be made available in a total of 3 variants. It gets a new 440cc, single-cylinder engine that puts out a rather impressive 27bhp and 38Nm of peak torque, thus making it more powerful than its direct rival Royal Enfield Classic 350. Our first ride review is coming soon, till then enjoy this walkaround.

snippet.description:

From 10th July onwards, Watch all your favourite serials exclusively ONLY on Sun NXT for FREE. *Free only for Indian Users.

Download here:
Android - http://bit.ly/SunNxtAdroid
iOS: India - http://bit.ly/sunNXT

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Vamsha Vruksham || A Family Comedy || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Vamsha Vriksham A Family Comedy MCM

Filmymoji releases “Vamsa Vruksham” one of the most hilarious episode ever where Middle class Madhu pays respect to his father like no other son in the history of father-son relationship would have ever done. Madhu and his mother highlights how they couldn’t sleep peacefully for the past few months because of his father’s snoring habit. They finally convince him to get some medication from the doctor. Madhu starts narrating about his father’s snoring habit to everyone to his father’s embarrassment. Watch the full episode to find out the sensational snoring story of our most sensible middle class family having the most senseless Middle class son.

snippet.title: Buldhana Bus Accident | बुलढाणा बस अपघातातील मृतांवर आज सामूहिक अंत्यसंस्कार | Marathi News
snippet.description:
Mass funeral for Buldhana accident victims. Malegaon will be led by BJP MLA Nilesh Rane, Hindu Janakrosh Morcha will be held. Chief Minister Eknath Shinde, Deputy Chief Minister Devendra Fadnavis inaugurated various works under Mira Bhayander Mahapalika. Amit Thackeray will go to Gangapur in Sambhajinagar to inaugurate a school. Gurupurnima festival begins in Shirdi.

बुलढाणा अपघातातील मृतांवर होणार सामूहिक अंत्यसंस्कार. मालेगावला भाजप आमदार निलेश राणे यांच्या नेतृत्वाखाली हिंदू जनआक्रोश मोर्चा काढण्यात येणार आहे. मुख्यमंत्री एकनाथ शिंदे, उपमुख्यमंत्री देवेंद्र फडणवीस यांच्या हस्ते मीरा भाईंदर नगरपालिका अंतर्गत विविध कामांच्या भूमिपूजन लोकार्पण सोहळा. अमित ठाकरे हे संभाजीनगरमध्ये गंगापूरला एका शाळेच्या लोकार्पपणासाठी जाणार आहेत.शिर्डीत गुरुपौर्णिमा उत्सवाला सुरूवात.

Episode 3813: Daya Ki Yaad
--------------------------------------------------------
Gokuldham men discuss their wives' dishes at Abdul's soda shop, while Taarak complains about his diet food. Popatlal complains about his bachelor life, and Jetha complains about his wife Daya avoiding him. Iyer makes a joke and advises Jetha to return to Daya. Jetha suddenly recalls his commitment to fast if Daya does not return within two months. Later, Champaklal and Tapu try to persuade Jetha to have Jalebi and Fafda, but he refuses. Will Daya ever return to the Gada family?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3813, 3 July 2023

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 18 Teaser - 3rd July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 18 Teaser - 3rd July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Nattu Kaka और Bagha को मिली Jetha से Party | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Lagataar
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Besides the money he usually mooches from Jethalal, Sundar has bigger plans this time. He fools Jethalal into paying him twelve thousand rupees and gives him mangoes in return. Moving on, Daya serves good food to everyone but eats simple food herself. This upsets Jethalal and out of emotions, he bends down in front of Daya. Later, all the ladies of the Gokuldham Society gather at Daya's house and makes her understand that everything will fall into place. But nothing can stop Daya from taking tensions for her brother!

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi
Episode - 829

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch the 'Comedy Lagataar' episodes from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZAg6W-3De1ssi64wfuZyw6

snippet.description:

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 637 | Samast Dwarka Prem Se Bholenath Ko Pukaaregi! #radhakrishn #starbharat 


राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 637 | Samast Dwarka Prem Se Bholenath Ko Pukaaregi! #radhakrishn #starbharat 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.title: Types of Relatives | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Prepare to be entertained as we explore the typical assortment of relatives who grace Indian families with their presence. From the loving yet overprotective siblings to the mischievous and ever-curious aunts and uncles, this sketch video hilariously captures the essence of these distinctive personalities. If you have faced the same type of situations or you belong to a type of category, do let us know in the comments.

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 735 & 736 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 735 & 736 | Recap

Alia tries persuading Harleen for permission to go to the summer camp. However, Harleen becomes concerned about Alia's safety and announces her decision not to send her to the summer camp. What will Alia do now?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

Pragati troubles Raghav to seek revenge on him. Later, Raghav gets shocked to see a changed avatar and is unable to understand, but Mehek learns his true identity and decides to use him to get Naaglok's treasure. Will she be successful in her plan?

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin 2nd Last Episode - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 28th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Song Lyrics :-

स्कीम स्कीम स्कीम
नीलकंठ त आयी स एक खबर बड़ी नमकीना भोलानाथ नोट छापण की सबनै दैव मशीन।
हाँ बच्चा नोट छापण की मशीन चाहिए,
 जी बाबा अच्छा अच्छा, 
बाबा बहोत दिन होगे मशीन मागते-भागते आज तो बाबा यो शुभ कार्य करै दो भगत को मशीन लाकै दो।
बाबा एक Request है, 
क्या Request है, 
बाबा हा - पाच दे दो, 
पाच मशीन, 
क्या करेगा पाच मशीनों का बाबा एक तो वो मेरी बेबे का छोरा है ना उस्तै दे प्यूगा अच्छा- अर एक मेरे मामा यी दे दयुगां, 
अर एक मेरा चाचा है. ना छोटे थाला वो भी गरीब सा ए आदमी है, 
एक उस्तै दे दयगे वो भी कमा रखा लेगा। हा हा अच्छा,
 एक मेरी माँ त्यी देदगे, 
एक मै / चला ट्यूगा,
 तेरी मौ चला लेगी, 
हा वा तो

साईकिल भी चला ले है। हा हा वाह रे भगत,
 वाह बेटा वाह,
 होगी ना पाच बाबा, 
मै कोए झूठ - बोलू मन्ने तो कोए ज्यादा लालच सा भी ना लेकिन बच्चा स्टोक मै त रही है।
 एक ही मशीन रह ना बाबा इब न्यू मतना करो फेर के बेरा आप कद आओगे, 
आज तो ले जाओ। क... न्यू मतना करो बाबा हवतो लगतै हाथा दे ये दो, 
एक मिलेगी, 
ना बाबा इब तो मै पाच ल्यूगा, 
पाच हा, एक मिलेगी, 
पाच ब्यूगा बाबा पाच ल्यूगा, 
बाबा, मशीन मागता होगा शर्म तो भाती नी होगी अरे पगली, 
आज मन्नै सुपने म बाबा दिखे है, 
अर सुबह का सपना कदै खाली नी जाया करे, 
चार साल होगे समझाती न क्यू मशीन के चक्कर मे पड़ा हुआ है और

क्यू और न मेर रखा है। बस थोड़ी सी
में गड़बड़ चालरी थी, आज शाम Calculation त्यी फैसला हो ज्यागा
बम भोले ओ..... बम मोले ओ.. बम-बम भोले बम बम भोले बम बम भोले
काम-धाम मै करता कोन्या साल हो लिए तीन मनै, 
काम करण का मूड ना बनता साल हो लिए तीन मन्नै भोलेनाथ नोट छापण कद-सी मिले मशीन मन्न।
भोलेनाथ नोट छापण की कद सी मिलै मशीन मनै । 
लगा-लगा क जोत बालदी या पूरा थी की दिन मनै, 
पक्की डेट बतादे भोते / कद सी मिले मशीन मनै- पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कदसी मिले मशीन मनै, 
बन भोते।
जिसकी किस्त नही भरनी हो इसा दवादे लोन मनै, 
ना करना पड़े रिचार्ज बाबा इसा


दवादे फोन मनै, मैं नोटा का प्यासा सू
बाबा धन का पाणी देदे नपी मशीन नही देता त मनै पुराणी देदे तू, कोए पुरापी दे दे तू। 
इमरू आले करणे होंगे सपने मेरे तू
रंगीन तनै, 
पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कद सी मिले मशीन मनै पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कद सी मिले मशीन मनै। 
सौ के नोट न भी बाबा मै कभी-कभी दिना चलाउ सूं, मारे पड़ोसी काजू चाब और मै बुगडे खाऊ सू,
थारी आरती गाते. गाते थूक मेरा यो सूख लिया, 
धूप लावण के चक्कर मे कभी व कुडता फूक बिया-कची ब कुड़ता फूक लिया, 
इस सिंहपरिये की जरूर सुर्णेगा सौ परशेट यकीन मनै,
 पक्की डेट बतादे भोबे कद सी मिले मशीन मनै-पक्की डेट बतादे भोले कद सी मिले मशीन मनै

भोले... र बच्चा चाहिए अगर मशीन वचन तनै भरणे होंगे तीन- वचन तन भरने धेरै तीन पहला वचन म छापने जितने छापे नोट, 
कभी मन मत ल्याइए खोट,
 मै ल्युगा डेली तेरी रिपोर्ट, करुगां हरकत सब तेरी नोट, 
अगर तनै घमंड दिखाया त, 
उनगर तनै चाप कमाया त,

मै कोए झूठ - बोलू मन्ने तो कोए ज्यादा लालच सा भी ना लेकिन बच्चा स्टोक मै त रही है।

snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 734 & 735 | Recap

Ekam experiences immense joy and happiness as Alia becomes a part of his life. However, when Harleen realises that Alia is Nehmat and Ekam's daughter, she vows to keep the truth hidden from everyone. Will Ekam ever learn the truth?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 635 | Krishn Bane Yagya Ke Yajmaan #radhakrishn #starbharat 

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3812 | 1 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3812: Mall Ke Daam
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena is having a good time playing football during the monsoon season, but things get worse when they accidently hit Bhide with their ball. Bhide falls and is injured the second time the ball hits him so hard. Bhide is taken to Dr. Hathi by Madhavi and the kids, who verify that he has a slight injury. Tapu Sena feels sorry for Bhide and decides to stop playing. They proceed to apologize to Bhide but are surprised to discover him dancing in joy. Bhide lied about his ailment to Tapu Sena in order to keep them from playing football. Later, while purchasing vegetables from Sunita's booth, the Gokuldham Ladies notice a new scheme.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3812, 1 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
